# PART 6 — DESIGN SYSTEM, SEO, ACCESSIBILITY & RESPONSIVE RULES

Kamiyon Studio Website Specification v2.0

---

## OBJECTIVE

The website should feel handcrafted — not a ThemeForest template. Every spacing choice, color, and component should communicate craftsmanship before visitors read a word.

**Theme:** Light mode only (Sakura internet reference + Kamiyon brand).

**Implementation:** Next.js 16, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4. Design tokens as CSS custom properties — see `context/ui-context.md`.

---

## DESIGN PRINCIPLES

| # | Principle | Rule |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Clarity | If it hurts readability, remove it |
| 2 | Breathing room | Whitespace is content; crowded layouts create anxiety |
| 3 | Proof over marketing | Every claim followed by evidence (work, logos, awards) |
| 4 | Editorial composition | Alternate layouts — never stack identical card grids repeatedly |
| 5 | Light first | White backgrounds, pink accents, dark text — no dark mode v1 |

