## INPUT FIELDS

(For any non-Google-Form inputs — search, filters)

- Rounded 16px, large touch target
- White background, soft border
- Hover: pink border
- Focus: pink glow ring, visible outline
- Label always visible (no placeholder-only labels)

---

## CARD SYSTEM

Structure:

```
Image (optional)
  ↓
Metadata / tags
  ↓
Title
  ↓
Description
  ↓
Action
```

- White surface, soft shadow, 16–24px radius
- Hover: lift + shadow increase
- Never clutter cards with too many fields

