### Responsive rules

| Component | Desktop | Mobile |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Hero | Split layout | Stacked |
| Card grids | 3 → 2 → 1 columns | 1 column |
| Navigation | Horizontal links | Hamburger |
| Portfolio bands | Full-width horizontal | Stacked, shorter height |
| Project detail | Gallery + sidebar | Stacked |
| Buttons | Auto width | Full width in forms/CTAs |

Images: intelligent crop, never stretch. `object-fit: cover` with defined aspect ratios.

---

## ACCESSIBILITY (WCAG AA)

| Requirement | Spec |
| --- | --- |
| Contrast | AA minimum all text/background pairs |
| Touch targets | 48px minimum |
| Keyboard | Full tab navigation, logical order |
| Focus | Visible focus ring (pink or high-contrast outline) |
| Headings | Semantic hierarchy, one H1 per page |
| Images | Descriptive alt text |
| Forms | Labels, error messages, aria attributes |
| Motion | `prefers-reduced-motion` respected |
| Color | Never sole indicator of state |

Test sakura pink on white and on overlay panels.

