## PERFORMANCE

| Target | Approach |
| --- | --- |
| LCP | Optimize hero image, priority load, next-gen formats |
| Images | WebP/AVIF, lazy-load below fold, responsive `srcset` |
| Fonts | `next/font` with subsetting |
| JS | Server components where possible; minimal client JS |
| Third party | Google Form iframe only on contact page |

