## SEO STRUCTURE

### Global

- Site title template: `%s | Kamiyon Studio`
- Default description from positioning canon (~150–160 chars)
- `robots.txt`, `sitemap.xml` generated at build
- Canonical URLs on all pages

### Per page

| Page | H1 | Meta focus |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Home | One hero headline | Creative technology studio, Philippines |
| Portfolio hub | Portfolio | Work across design, games, illustration… |
| Category | {Category} | Discipline-specific keywords |
| Project | {Project name} | Project-specific description |
| News | News | Studio news and announcements |
| About | About Kamiyon Studio | Story, team, mission |
| Press | Press Kit | Media resources |
| Contact | Contact | Get in touch, project inquiries |

### Structured data (JSON-LD)

- `Organization` on all pages (site-wide)
- `WebSite` on home
- `BreadcrumbList` on portfolio category + project pages
- `FAQPage` on contact if FAQ present

### Open Graph

- Unique `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image` per page
- Project pages: project hero image
- Default: logo or brand banner from `docs/assets/`

### Keywords (natural, no stuffing)

Game development Philippines, creative technology, interactive experiences, Unity, design studio, illustration, branding, 3D animation, web design

