## CONTENT WRITING RULES

**Never use:** cutting-edge, innovative, world-class, disruptive, industry-leading, game-changing

**Prefer:** thoughtful, crafted, reliable, player-focused, collaborative, purposefully built, meaningful

**Buttons:** action-oriented, short

**Forms:** "Tell us about your project."

