## ANIMATION (v1)

Ship minimal interaction only:

- Button/card hover states
- FAQ accordion open/close
- Thumbnail gallery swap
- Nav shadow on scroll

Prepare CSS for future fade/scale reveals. Nothing depends on animation to function.

