## DESIGN QA CHECKLIST

Before marking any page complete:

- [ ] Hierarchy obvious at a glance?
- [ ] Primary CTA visible and reachable?
- [ ] Enough whitespace — would Apple remove anything?
- [ ] Every marketing claim backed by proof on the same page or linked?
- [ ] Light mode consistent — no accidental dark sections?
- [ ] Pink accent used sparingly (~15%)?
- [ ] Responsive at 390px and 1440px?
- [ ] WCAG AA contrast pass?
- [ ] All images have alt text?
- [ ] Canon facts only — placeholders labeled?
- [ ] `npm run build` passes?

